desc_short	-----								Aerofly FS 2 Flight Simulator lets you explore the world of flying in a quality never seen before. Fly a large selection of highly detailed aircraft with interactive 3D cockpits. Aerofly FS 2 currently features over 150 airports in the south western USA and global elevation and satellite imagery.							
